{"tid":1614370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣升級]仲po fact news? 開始學整MEME圖同畫政治漫畫啦","createTime":"2019-10-02T18:26:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T06:39:13.000Z","uid":235465,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e9271b23bb8a1d875d17119a8cde012260b9d95b","tid":1614370,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:26:04.000Z","msg":"背景:發現好多人上twitter到就po段片+一段fact news 黎retweet<br />\n但其實你地咁做 9成時間會變成自己喂威喂<br />\n因為要睇fact news 大部分時間會選擇睇新聞報紙 而po上去瘋狂洗對件事無咩幫助<br />\n簡單D 你瘋狂loop 段&quot;fact&quot;片 人地只會覺得你hard sell緊 唔吸引<br />\n<br />\n所以 其實可以做一個步驟:幽默化 令自己D野&quot;更容易入口&quot; 更可以懶人化<br />\n當然唔代表要完全停止fact news<br />\n最好retweet fact news+附上自己整嘅MEME圖/漫畫<br />\n<br />\n但政治漫畫需要本人畫功同靈感上唔差先做到 相反對政客/老一輩比較關心政治黎講威力比較大(因為處理細節位 比meme圖變化多好多)<br />\n<br />\n下面MEME圖舉個例子:<br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/603/0*EjEdevp7kEmwl00d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F603%2F0%2AEjEdevp7kEmwl00d.png&h=07973a79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相反 ,政治漫畫其實買少見少 因為政治冷感個問題好嚴重<br />\n搵極得li張台灣人畫 OK有意義<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpLvJwRu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpLvJwRu.jpg&h=0d18f8c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而政治漫畫最強力一點<br />\nMEME圖最多可以將<span style=\"color: red;\">現有事實</span>幽默化<br />\n但政治漫畫發揮得好 可以將宜家以及<span style=\"color: red;\">預測未來發生事</span>畫埋出黎<br />\n例如 今日班狗開得第一槍 如果你用政治漫畫黎表達 你可以畫埋把MP5係&quot;未來&quot;到<br />\n或者大家都講 今日香港 明日世界 同樣可以以政治漫畫黎表達<br />\n當然 強調一次 對畫功幾有要求 因為一幅好政治漫畫重於細節<br />\n<br />\n另外 如果對以上兩種&quot;升級文宣&quot;都無idea 咁可以繼續po fact片<br />\n但假設如果比較後做retweet動作 可以將文字幽默化 唔單單要&quot;陳述事實&quot;<br />\nli樣連登做開 簡單D將你句野膠化 但又唔好太膠"},{"pid":"ec2e200b4b2390efc74c96f31b7659b6271d84b1","tid":1614370,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48a39697ec4e1dda8c3dadd9b0cb612c9edf413","tid":1614370,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d948fdb0e437a782be29e15c93c22af32db59d6","tid":1614370,"uid":235465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpsdbPFL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpsdbPFL.jpg&h=37429ea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n順便舉多個例 政治漫畫例子"},{"pid":"ac1880da9596f0b776af6523a59e8840a6f0de1c","tid":1614370,"uid":63127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:30:10.000Z","msg":"政治漫畫真係唔易畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋國際傳開既話本身都要了解左d news先會睇得明漫畫，相輔相成啦"},{"pid":"f51849515f0dac83ee9f58bf611b5dd5004ad9e9","tid":1614370,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac1880da9596f0b776af6523a59e8840a6f0de1c","tid":1614370,"uid":63127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:30:10.000Z","msg":"政治漫畫真係唔易畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋國際傳開既話本身都要了解左d news先會睇得明漫畫，相輔相成啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:48:20.000Z","msg":"其實可以從易入手<br />\n例如&quot;冷戰&quot; 共產主義入侵 代表第二次冷戰或者第二次共產危機等等<br />\nli類外國人會比較有個模知咩事<br />\n再吸引佢地令佢地了解後再深入<br />\n<br />\n有idea但無畫功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81fe90605642f286fe6694ab0588e7044057eb2b","tid":1614370,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:48:33.000Z","m